latestPosts.caption:
From childhood giggles to wedding bells, so proud of the beautiful bride you’ve become. Forever my sister, now a stunning wife🧿🤍

Sometimes it can feel like life is just you against the world but lucky for me it never felt like that, from the moment I’ve opened by eyes to now I’ve had a shield: my sister, 
 
You deserve the world and I can’t wait to see all the magical things you do starting this new journey of your life. I love you to no ends and I’m gonna be here for you till our very last breaths🤍

Always had a fear of losing my shield but the moment I met Kunal jeej I realised I was gaining one🤍

Kunal jeej you’ve quite literally come into our lives as a backbone, brother and a best friend.  From making sure I have my life on track, to my workouts, diet and every other minute detail.

I’ve never been so confident about giving  my sister away but hats off you’ve ticked all and many more boxes. Welcome to the family Kunzi, love you way more than you know!

I hope you enjoy growing old with her as much I’ve enjoyed growing up with her🧿🤍
